---
name: New Project
description: Request a large chunk of work comprised of multiple deliverables
labels: ["Type: Project"]
body:
  - type: input
    id: vault_link
    attributes:
      label: Vault link
      placeholder: e.g. https://vault.shopify.io/gsd/projects/12345
  - type: textarea
    id: description
    attributes:
      label: Description
      description: Several lines or short paragraphs that summarize the problem being solved or the opportunity being captured.  This should be enough for general Shopifolk without prior knowledge to understand what is being done and why.  (This could be copied from the Vault GSD project)
  - type: dropdown
    id: product_area
    attributes:
      label: Teams
      options:
        - Plus
        - Money
        - Retail
        - Markets
        - Audiences
        - Paid D&V
        - Paid Social 
        - Affiliates 
  - type: textarea
    id: tasks
    attributes:
      label: Tasks
      description: Define the initial list of anticipated deliverables.  These will evolve as work progresses, so only capture what you know now (or just leave it as-is).
      value: |
        ```[tasklist]
        ### Deliverables 
        - [ ] ...
        ```
---
